問其他問題<br />\n如是者佢兩個成晚係個group冇停過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你同得個客講話呢幾日係我follow佢啲野<br />\n係咪應該交返俾我做呢？<br />\n總之你返到黎我report返俾你知咪得<br />\n好似驚死我坐係到乜都唔做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你搏表現唔緊要<br />\n但有冇係其他同事立場諗過？<br />\n你咁做係想話俾人聽我工作唔上心？我話唔到事？你好緊張個客？<br />\n第一，放假都掛住公司野老闆唔會多謝你，只會令佢覺得咁係老馮<br />\n第二，遲啲覆個客唔會死，當晚覆定聽朝覆對成件事冇影響"},{"pid":"69f341e8a13d89373c46e24ce83b98876dc5ad66","tid":712031,"uid":66887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a8e5241c1036c5f2924620596685fce4c9f5778","tid":712031,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"90ac2bfd19a4db07d36676c0717086e376589875","tid":712031,"uid":57549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a1fa8d520e3ef6826992bece711dc8687671cb64","tid":712031,"uid":164920,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:09:36.000Z","msg":"明明好小事，仲緊張過老細，搞到成個office啲氣氛疆晒，煩過閪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:20:26.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n同有啲開口埋口話要為公司著想一樣咁撚戇鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T00:22:21.000Z","msg":"佢地個理論係：無自己做醜人，公司永遠唔會有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:29:55.000Z","msg":"哩種人 通常係是非精<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日掉返轉d野來講<br />\n見高拜見低踩"},{"pid":"1ff44fcdd35a8aed39c9cd2eb73bcc3e0cafe739","tid":712031,"uid":66887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0104c0112a8661e398b714ea7e21ada7989a1b6a","tid":712031,"uid":171594,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"